    91→%                                                                             %
    92→%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
    93→%
    94→%  CropToFitImage() crops the sheared image as determined by the bounding box
    95→%  as defined by width and height and shearing angles.
    96→%
    97→%  The format of the CropToFitImage method is:
